data.description: Newly constructed 2020 concrete home with 3 beds, 2 baths, and a 2-car garage. Enjoy the open floor plan with wood plank tile and carpet in bedrooms. The kitchen is equipped with solid wood cabinets, granite countertops, an island, and stainless steel appliances. The family room seamlessly connects to the kitchen and dining area, leading to a covered patio. The master bedroom features a coffered ceiling and walk-in closet, and the master bath includes a tiled walk-in shower, garden tub, and granite vanity. The guest bath has a tub/shower combo. Impact glass windows ensure safety, and the fenced backyard offers space for a boat/RV. The Rails to Trails path is just 400 feet away, and two local boat ramps are nearby. Conveniently close to Daytona shopping, Titus Landing outdoor mall, and the space center.
